display_long_description:
Are you ready to push your limits?

Overstep is a pulse-pounding VR parkour challenge designed for those who love a true test of skill. While the goal is simple—get from start to finish—the journey is anything but easy. Navigate through 11 meticulously crafted levels that demand precision, timing, and nerves of steel.

Why play Overstep?

11 Challenging Levels: Progress through stages that evolve from "tricky" to "nearly impossible."

Precision Gameplay: Experience a pure parkour mechanic where every jump and landing counts.

Smart Checkpoints: Don't lose all your progress! Our checkpoint system ensures you can jump back into the action after a fall.

Hardcore Difficulty: Designed for players who miss the era of games that provided a real challenge. No hand-holding here.

Immersive VR Design: Clean visuals and intuitive controls that keep you focused on the next jump.

Do you have what it takes to reach the final platform? Download Overstep today and prove your agility!
